title: no 10 year rewards
body:
a rioter posted that co-op counted as a game to receive rewards, so i played a co-op and i also played a pvp aram

i have not received kalye, riot kayle, or the 10 year icon

replies.body: The gifts are not yet done being distributed. The final day to receive them is the 23rd, so if you do not receive them by then, you can submit a support ticket.

Yup, as *Zombiemaster* mentioned, we're still sending these out.

Let me know if you don't have anything by the *23rd*.
